        <abstract> 
<p>Offers CD a live <hi rend="italic">Proteus anguinus</hi> from Adelsberg cave. In his hands it will have a fair chance of developing into "some type of Columbidae (say a pouter or tumbler)".</p>  
<p>The <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> is universally praised in Italy and Germany, even by those who disagree with it.</p> 
